{"tid":2046890,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"防菌/防UV！日本推可重用和紙纖維口罩　3個月內可分解成植物養份","createTime":"2020-06-01T17:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T23:34:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94a1e6985bd4f4a516f5fb06c449b82c2e9cf5a9","tid":2046890,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holiday.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/reusemask.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Freusemask.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830&h=5f4e6ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然現時疫情已冇之前咁嚴重，但口罩對現時嚟講暫時仲未可以脫離大家嘅日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n不過一次性口罩喺作為一件唔環保嘅必需品時，唔少人都會來嚟一啲比較環保嘅可重用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n早前日本就有公司喺網站「makuake」眾籌，推出一款以符合世界安全水平證明嘅纖維製作，不含化學染色物，漂白劑，既不傷害肌膚亦能保護環境嘅和紙口罩「paper」。<br />\n<br />\n目前依款口罩已經眾籌成功並已投入生產，但就只可以喺日本買到，如果大家有興趣可能就要諗吓計喇！"},{"pid":"b1ad6585e556db0df30448a9daa54a96fd92b245","tid":2046890,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/183711/防菌-防uv-日本推可重用和紙纖維口罩%E3%80%803個月內可分解成植物養份\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Farticle%2F183711%2F%E9%98%B2%E8%8F%8C-%E9%98%B2uv-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%8F%AF%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%92%8C%E7%B4%99%E7%BA%96%E7%B6%AD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%25E3%2580%25803%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%88%90%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%8A%E4%BB%BD&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns81gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=d3703ca3\" target=\"_blank\">https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/183711/防菌-防uv-日本推可重用和紙纖維口罩%E3%80%803個月內可分解成植物養份</a>"},{"pid":"f331d3fcfeaf94d108d6ef182353a87d2aebca19","tid":2046890,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"唔防病毒，完"},{"pid":"de2b1268170513e28b3c1dafe2b4a18dcabb4fd9","tid":2046890,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike